aggregationbotton: Groups all Formulas by the Document they belong to
openall: Opens all the containers with search results
closeall: Closes all the containers with search results
goup: Scroll to top of the page
godown: Scroll to bottom of the page
size: Changes the number of formulas that are fetched in single request. (pay attention big numbers here may take really long)
showmore: Fetch the next batch of results
examples: Shows a list of examples queries
symbols: Shows a list of possible symbols that can be used in a query
